She's pissed about losing her match against, featherweight, Lyla Storm and she's been training so that she can whoop some ass and get some pussy as her prize.
Wenona has taken some time off from wrestling and is suffering from ring rust. However she still knows how to put on that brutal headlock she's turned into her signature move. Rilynn has done her homework. She knows about Wenona's headlock and she's trained defense.
The Two clash on our mats for 2 full rounds. An injury is cause to stop this match early in round 3 just before one of the wrestlers is caught in a hold that leaves her whimpering and an too frustrated to cum.***************************
check out the indepth post match interview for some interesting facts about these two wrestlers never before discussed!!!
